{
  "text": "Many interesting approaches for pedestrian detection have been proposed, for a survey see [CITATION_1] . Most work has pursued a learning-based approach, bypassing a pose recovery step and describing human appearance directly in terms of simple low-level features from a region of interest (ROI) .",
